knows what to do.} Qxb2 6. Rb1 Qxa2 7. Rxb7 e6 8. Ne2 $1 (8. Bd3 $6 Bxd3 9.
cxd3 {took place in Zvjaginsev - Rozum, EU-ch, Yerevan, 2014, when} Qa6 $1 10.
