A pseudo-classical central strategy like} 10. Nge4 {does not achieve much
against correct play, such as} Nh6 $1 11. Bxh6 Rxh6 {and, as the following
examples are demonstrating, very experienced English grandmasters did not get
anything substantial out of the opening:} 12. Qe2 (12. Qd2 {took place in
