} 11. Bf4 Nh6 $5 {is fully playable, this idea is going to be implemented in
leading text as well. Black has enough counterplay, though precision is
required:} 12. Qd2 (12. Rc1 Nf5 (12... Rd8 $5 {, putting the central d-pawn
